<li class='toclevel-1'><a href="/web/20080608025104/http://www.modwiki.net/wiki/Extending_the_Area_Awareness_System#Setup_Code"><span class="tocnumber">2</span> <span class="toctext">Setup Code</span></a></li>
<li class='toclevel-1'><a href="/web/20080608025104/http://www.modwiki.net/wiki/Extending_the_Area_Awareness_System#Adding_Elevator_Reachabilities"><span class="tocnumber">3</span> <span class="toctext">Adding Elevator Reachabilities</span></a></li>
<li class='toclevel-1'><a href="/web/20080608025104/http://www.modwiki.net/wiki/Extending_the_Area_Awareness_System#Elevator_Screenshots"><span class="tocnumber">4</span> <span class="toctext">Elevator Screenshots</span></a></li>
