<p>When Init is called on each idAAS the actual work to find and add the extensions is done. For now the only file that is processed is the aas48 file. If someone wants to incorporate the player class changing code we could have bots with any model, and any AAS size. If you do this, you will need to change the check to include the appropriate extension. other modifications later may also be necessary.
</p>
