<span style="color: #000000;">&#125;</span></pre>
<p>This type of pattern will continue until each spot in the bottom rotation has been checked against each spot in the top rotation, and the first and last portals have also been connected. Finally, if all the coagulation above couldn’t create something usable, one last attempt is made creating a portal that doesn’t REALLY share an edge between two clusters, but it works&nbsp;;)
</p>
<pre>&nbsp;
	<span style="color: #0000ff;">if</span> <span style="color: #000000;">&#40;</span>&nbsp;!reachabilityCreated <span style="color: #000000;">&#41;</span> <span style="color: #000000;">&#123;</span>
